29:24.560 --> 29:28.000
♪ No money back, no guarantee

29:28.080 --> 29:31.000
♪ Black or white, rich or poor

29:31.080 --> 29:35.440
♪ We'll cut prices at a stroke!

29:35.760 --> 29:38.960
♪ God bless Hookey Street!

29:39.040 --> 29:41.960
♪ Viva Hookey Street!

29:42.040 --> 29:44.520
